title: Twitter Exposes WikiLeaks Court Order
description: The US Justice Department obtained a court order, directing Twitter to turn over information about the accounts of activists with ties to Wikileaks, including IP addresses, e-mail and residential addresses, billing records and details of bank accounts and credit cards. Cato Institute's Julian Sanchez explains.
